        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks for photograph, charmed by Mrs Huxley’s letter.</p>
            <p>Regrets THH cannot do the popular work on zoology.</p> 
<p>Has heard THH wrote leading article in last <hi rend="italic">Reader</hi> ["Science and ""church policy"" ", 4 (1864): 821].</p> 
        </abstract>
